room_title: Escape room "The Lab 51" by Exit Game in Los Angeles
room_address: 111 N. Atlantic Blvd., #148  Monterey Park, CA 91754
room_description: As part of an elite military strike force, your squad has one hour to infiltrate Lab 51 and to find out what happened to the alien life form within the lab. The lab is set to self-destruct in one hour so time is important. Discover the secrets of conspiracy theories on what really is in the alien lab!
